sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant T as Ticker (5 min)
    participant DC as Data Collector
    participant MC as Metrics Collector
    participant LC as Logs Collector
    participant DB as Dataset Builder
    participant P as Prometheus
    participant K as K8s API
    participant CSV as CSV File

    Note over T, CSV: Data Collection Cycle

    T->>DC: Trigger Collection
    DC->>DB: CollectUnifiedData(5min)
    
    rect rgb(180, 210, 240)
        Note right of DB: Phase 1: Collect Metrics
        DB->>K: List Pods (default namespace)
        K-->>DB: Pod List
        DB->>MC: GetPodMetrics()
        MC->>P: Query container_cpu_usage
        P-->>MC: CPU: 0.45 cores
        MC->>P: Query container_memory_usage
        P-->>MC: Memory: 128 MB
        MC-->>DB: Metrics Data
    end

    rect rgb(255, 220, 180)
        Note right of DB: Phase 2: Collect Logs
        DB->>LC: CollectAllPodsLogs(since 5m)
        LC->>K: GetLogs for each pod
        K-->>LC: Raw Logs
        LC->>LC: Parse logs (count errors)
        LC-->>DB: LogStats {errors: 12, requests: 450}
    end

    rect rgb(180, 240, 180)
        Note right of DB: Phase 3: Build Dataset
        DB->>DB: Merge Metrics + Logs
        DB->>DB: Calculate error rate, CPU%
        DB->>DB: Label data (IsHealthy)
        DB->>CSV: WriteToCSV(dataPoints)
        CSV-->>DB: ✓ Written
    end
    
    DB-->>DC: Success (N points)
    DC-->>T: Wait for next cycle
